<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Finish Your ISA Dental Account</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0; 
        padding: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7fafc;
      }
      .header-banner {
        background: #337ab7; /* or your brand color (#2B6CB0, etc.) */
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 24px;
      }
      .heading {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #2d3748;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px; 
        line-height: 1.5; 
        color: #4a5568; 
        margin: 0 0 16px;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        background: #2B6CB0;   /* Button background */
        color: #ffffff !important;        /* White text for better visibility */
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        transition: background 0.2s ease;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background: #1E40AF;  /* Slightly darker on hover */
        color: #ffffff;       /* Keep text white on hover */
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 24px; 
        font-size: 14px; 
        color: #a0aec0; 
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="header-banner">
      ISA Dental
    </div>

    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <h1 class="heading">Welcome to ISA Dental!</h1>
      <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

      <p>
        We’ve created an account for you. To finish setting up your account and choose your
        password, please click the button below:
      </p>

      <p>
        <a class="btn" href="<%= @invitation_url %>" target="_blank">
          Finish Your Account Setup
        </a>
      </p>

      <p>If the button isn’t working, copy and paste this link in your browser:</p>
      <p><%= @invitation_url %></p>

      <p>We look forward to helping you with all your dental needs!</p>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> ISA Dental &mdash; All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
